race.comment: Dead-set weak. FUTURE HERO (3) speared to the lead from a wide alley before fading out of it over 2150m at Ipswich last time. Unplaced the two outings prior but those efforts read well enough for this contest. Has a low gate and gets his opportunity. JADATAN (5) finished a well-beaten fourth against the above at Ipswich at big odds. That was an improved effort and she can't be ruled out in this lineup. VISCOUNT SYDNEY (7) tries had and keeps the handy 2kg claim. His best form would see him in the finish. RED VEGAS (6) has been struggling but is in light with the 2kg claim and can't entirely be dismissed in a race of low calibre.
